<bibRefCitation id="6B2900ADFF94FFEEFF2FFE9F4DDDFEE8" author="ROUGEMONT G" box="[185,384,352,374]" pageId="14" pageNumber="1585" pagination="713 - 736" refId="ref7829" refString="ROUGEMONT G. de (1996): Stiliderus and Stilicoderus: New data and new species (Coleoptera, Staphylinidae, Paederinae). - Revue Suisse de Zoologie 103 (3): 713 - 736." type="journal article" year="1996">ROUGEMONT 1996</bibRefCitation>
